{"arkId":"cl010111703","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010111703","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Coffret servant d\u0027encrier","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Coffret servant d\u0027encrier"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Renaissance (Occident)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 2796 1","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"encrier","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Il affecte la forme d\u0027un coffret rectangulaire allong\u00e9, port\u00e9 sur quatre pieds form\u00e9s de sir\u00e8nes dont le corps se termine par des volutes. Les flancs sont garnis de godrons et d\u0027une frise de palmettes se d\u00e9tachant en relief sur un fond mat\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u0027outil. Le couvercle, l\u00e9g\u00e8rement bomb\u00e9, \u00e0 quatre pans, est d\u00e9cor\u00e9 de feuillages ; au centre, deux cornes d\u0027abondance nou\u00e9es par des banderoles accompagnaient une t\u00eate de M\u00e9duse qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 lim\u00e9e. A l\u0027int\u00e9rieur, trois compartiments.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"9","displayDimension":"9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"23","displayDimension":"23 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"14","displayDimension":"14 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : bronze (patine noire. Trois compartiments \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur avec traces d\u0027oxydation. Les compartiments et le fond fondus avec le reste. La prise en forme d\u0027enfant portant un \u00e9cu a \u00e9t\u00e9 retir\u00e9 et inventori\u00e9e \u00e0 part)\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal","placeOfCreation":"Italie (Europe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection du baron Charles Davillier (1823-1883) ; legs Davillier, 1883","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Baron Davillier, Jean-Charles","note":"","role":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1883","startYear":1883,"endYear":1883}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs"}],"period":[{"value":"Renaissance"}],"place":[{"value":"Italie"}],"objectType":[{"value":"encrier"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Malgouyres, Philippe, De Filarete \u00e0 Riccio. Bronzes italiens de la Renaissance (1430-1550). La collection du Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Paris, Louvre Editions ; Mare \u0026 Martin, 2020","bibliographyDate":"2020","bibliographyDetail":"p. 348, n\u00b0 212","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Migeon, Gaston, Catalogue des bronzes et cuivres de la Renaissance et des temps modernes, Paris, Librairies-imprimeries r\u00e9unies, 1904","bibliographyDate":"1904","bibliographyDetail":"p. 116, n\u00b0 86","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Courajod, Louis ; Molinier, Emile, Donation du baron Charles Davillier. Catalogue des objets expos\u00e9s au mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Paris, Imprimeries r\u00e9unies, 1885, Disponible sur : \u0026lt;https:\/\/gallica.bnf.fr\/ark:\/12148\/bpt6k12659088\/f1.item\u0026gt; ","bibliographyDate":"1885","bibliographyDetail":"p. 80, n\u00b0 109","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cach